#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.240"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.240:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.240:0.2"
msgid "24. Āvāsikavagga"
msgstr "24. A Resident Mendicant"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.240:0.3"
msgid "240. Dutiyamacchariyasutta"
msgstr "240. Stinginess (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.240:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato āvāsiko bhikkhu yathābhataṃ "
"nikkhitto evaṃ niraye."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a resident mendicant with five qualities is cast down to hell."

msgctxt "an5.240:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.240:1.3"
msgid "Āvāsamaccharī hoti;"
msgstr "They’re stingy regarding monasteries,"

msgctxt "an5.240:1.4"
msgid "kulamaccharī hoti;"
msgstr "families,"

msgctxt "an5.240:1.5"
msgid "lābhamaccharī hoti;"
msgstr "material possessions,"

msgctxt "an5.240:1.6"
msgid "vaṇṇamaccharī hoti;"
msgstr "praise,"

msgctxt "an5.240:1.7"
msgid "dhammamaccharī hoti."
msgstr "and the teachings."

msgctxt "an5.240:1.8"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato āvāsiko bhikkhu "
"yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye."
msgstr "A resident mendicant with these five qualities is cast down to hell."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.267"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.240:2.1"
msgid ""
"Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato āvāsiko bhikkhu yathābhataṃ "
"nikkhitto evaṃ sagge."
msgstr "A resident mendicant with five qualities is raised up to heaven."

msgctxt "an5.240:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.240:2.3"
msgid "Na āvāsamaccharī hoti;"
msgstr "They’re not stingy regarding monasteries,"

msgctxt "an5.240:2.4"
msgid "na kulamaccharī hoti;"
msgstr "families,"

msgctxt "an5.240:2.5"
msgid "na lābhamaccharī hoti;"
msgstr "material possessions,"

msgctxt "an5.240:2.6"
msgid "na vaṇṇamaccharī hoti;"
msgstr "praise,"

msgctxt "an5.240:2.7"
msgid "na dhammamaccharī hoti."
msgstr "and the teachings."

msgctxt "an5.240:2.8"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato āvāsiko bhikkhu "
"yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge”ti."
msgstr "A resident mendicant with these five qualities is raised up to heaven.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.240:2.9"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.240:2.10"
msgid "Āvāsikavaggo catuttho."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
#. VAR: piyo ca sobhano → ābhāvanīyo piyasobhanā ca (bj) | āvāsiko appiyasobhanā ca (s1-3)
msgctxt "an5.240:3.1"
msgid "Āvāsiko piyo ca sobhano,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.240:3.2"
msgid "Bahūpakāro anukampako ca;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an5.240:3.3"
msgid "Tayo avaṇṇārahā ceva,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
#. VAR: Macchariyā duvepi cāti → yathābhataṃ cādi tayo avaṇṇārahā duve macchariyā ca vuttā (bj) | catukkamaccherapañcakena cāti (si, s1-3) | catukkamacchariyena cāti (pts1) | catuko macchariyena cāti (mr)
msgctxt "an5.240:3.4"
msgid "Macchariyā duvepi cāti."
msgstr ""
